Subject: Re: [RFC][PATCH 1/4] add jiffies_to_nsecs() helper and fix up size of usecs
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
